27_spill_effects_visualization

Markus Min

2023-07-13

Description

This Rmd will investigate patterns of fallback with spill, to examine what the data thats going into the model looks like.

Note that this Rmd only contains wild, Upper Columbia steelhead for consistency with the modeling results

This parameter should be assigned to Wenatchee and Entiat fish.
